# Mobile / tablet / landscape QA (MyDSP style)

Encode these preferences so future agents do **not** reintroduce clutter or overlapping chrome.

## Thumb CTA bars (phone + short landscape)

- `.thumb-cta-bar` is for **primary create actions only** (Add X, Mark all read, Retry unavailable). One row preferred; wrap is OK only for 2–4 essential buttons.
- **Never** duplicate Format / density / Expand / Collapse / Sort controls into the thumb bar — those live in page toolbars / disclosure panels.
- **Never** put page-level **Refresh** / **Sync now** in thumb bars (see `clean-sync-refresh-ux.mdc`). Non-interactive “Refreshing data” status is fine.
- Spacer height must use **measured** `--thumb-cta-height` (ResizeObserver), not a hardcoded `4.25rem` alone.
- Keep thumb CTAs available in **landscape phone** (`orientation: landscape` + short height), not only `max-width: 639px`.

## No overlapping fixed chrome

- Fixed bars (thumb CTA, Job Detail action bar, bottom nav, floating banners/toasts) must **stack with measured offsets** — never guess two fixed heights that can wrap and collide.
- Floating banners/toasts clear `--thumb-cta-height` as well as the bottom nav.
- Job Detail: measure `--job-detail-action-height`; nav CTA sits above the action bar.

## Sticky stacks

- App header height → `--app-header-offset` (measured from `.app-header`, includes sync strip / meta).
- Markets sticky Tag/Yield filters sit **under** `--markets-toolbar-height`, not at the same `top` as the toolbar.
- Do **not** put `overflow: hidden` on `.app-header-row` / `.toolbar-cluster` — it clips More / Notifications menus.

## Markets chrome

- Prefer disclosure panels (Assets / Timeframe / Format) over permanent chip rows.
- Default timeframe **24H**; quiet poll ~**60s**; no noisy “Showing n/m prices” status; no useless Markets search.
- Section add buttons cover commodity / FX / index — thumb stays Add equity + Add crypto (+ conditional holding / retry).

## Tablet (≥sm)

- When thumb bars hide, PageHeader (or section empty states) must still expose primary Add actions.
- Portrait **and** landscape must both remain usable — equal priority with phone.

## Visual / UX style (carry forward)

- Minimal clear chrome; no overlapping buttons; full Edit pencils (no clipped icons).
- Cross-device sync for YouTube / News / Markets is imperative.
- Headers: Prices/section eyebrows+titles match My Crypto title scale.
